{"tid":1439042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"那夜凌晨我上了藍屍廢老嘅的士","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:21:58.000Z","uid":294427,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f56fe58341ce716707ef34f14f606248e7e594d2","tid":1439042,"uid":294427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"我屌 成程車就係咁聽佢鳩up<br />\n又話乜撚野前線全部收錢 有500美金一日<br />\n又話乜撚野前十排個啲嘅口罩係大會派 <br />\n浸過蛋白清<br />\n搞到啲人吸左之後會好抗奮 好勇鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我聽到真係屌哂老母 姐刻問佢500美金收賣一個人出去俾狗打 仲要冒風險俾狗告暴動要坐10年？我屌佢竟然答我話份糧包左 之後佢又屌9我地冇讀過書 我見佢講到好激動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就廢事同佢嘈 事關個陣過緊青馬大橋<br />\n巧驚佢嬲起上尼衝落海就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2e8216f0e8b648afffc4905a59afb838e9c6b5","tid":1439042,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:54:19.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6d85d9607bba8c653d6bada769a9d6f4483e23b6","tid":1439042,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰 **不指揮**</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439078</a>"},{"pid":"4805fe125a2da734f63fff2e57d1fef94f050f78","tid":1439042,"uid":46822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"藍蛆d邏輯係正常人完全跟唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0224a8dff54b13f57473c113f7ec78c24ee907dd","tid":1439042,"uid":5288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"同佢講<br />\n我俾500$美金你出去啦<br />\n佢實話唔會<br />\n咁你就可以順利成章<br />\n「你個樣咁撚柒碌又無撚腦，俾$500美金你都唔肯出啦，何況有腦嘅人？」"},{"pid":"5470dddc987e9f863713e8c2455d56056e6ab01f","tid":1439042,"uid":81389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:14:07.000Z","msg":"我比500美金佢比我用棍扑同打丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c61838f3924bc5a011e2d015349236715f7cd56","tid":1439042,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"}]}